						"elementDisplay": {
							"value": "<p chunk_id=\"b66b9897-bb27-4823-8060-1ea290d8506d\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong> Speak the First Ideal</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"607f9450-58b7-4af9-8b06-a40aec98265a\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Two Actions\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Two Actions\">2</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"9fd0fc00-d327-4ad8-952d-8011fc0c7e1f\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You use Regrowth to rapidly recover injuries, including permanent ones and missing body parts.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"04c29951-2492-4847-b271-e4032591d606\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body ParaOverride-2\">Spend 2 Investiture to cause yourself or a willing character you touch to instantly recover from a temporary injury of the target’s choice, or spend 3 Investiture to recover from a permanent <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"injuries\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">injury</tooltip>.</p>",
							"matchLevel": "none",
							"matchedWords": []
						},
						"name": {
							"value": "Injury Regrowth",
							"matchLevel": "none",
							"matchedWords": []
						},
						"shortDescription": {
							"value": "You use Regrowth to rapidly recover injuries, including permanent ones and missing body parts.",
							"matchLevel": "none",
							"matchedWords": []
						}
					}
				},
				{
					"dataType": "talent",
					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"df8ee8e8-7834-4d78-867a-c11b269429d8\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong>\n<tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"explosive-growth\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Explosive Growth</tooltip> talent\n</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"199536d2-d473-4c20-87e9-8250842a1b39\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Always Active\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Always Active\">∞</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"4bddbe27-4536-4d39-8b2c-758dbd86f7a7\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You persuade plants to grow beyond their normal size and shape.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"32ca4c7c-ee8d-444b-a23e-d856b5c3f0be\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">When you infuse Growth into a plant, you can make a DC 15 Progression test as part of that action. On a success, you cause the plant to grow beyond its species’ normal limits, up to the surge size for your ranks in Progression, and the plant’s current and total health increase by 2d4. The size of these dice increases with your ranks in Progression; at 2 ranks, roll 2d6 (instead of 2d4), and so on.</p>",
